# Phase 4 cross-service correlation demo fixture.
#
# Services used: order-service → payment-service → bank-gateway
# (all in the same connected component per config/dependencies.yaml)
#
# Scenario: bank-gateway goes down, causing cascading failures upstream.
#
# Expected output:
#   Windows 1-3: baseline establishment — all patterns flagged [NEW]
