#     The correlator groups them into ONE incident:
#       root cause: bank-gateway (depth=2, deepest)
#       dep chain: bank-gateway → payment-service → order-service
#
# Config: use config/config-correlator.yaml
# Run:    cd log_agent && go run ./cmd/agent/ config/config-correlator.yaml
# Total run time: ~25s (4 × 6s pauses + log processing)

